@startuml access_auth_to_door_fr_unlock_gate_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Access Auth To Door FR Unlock Gate Signal Flow\n(front-door control + access authorization -> DOOR_FR unlock gate)

participant "Door-control bus" as DoorCtl #F4F7FB
participant "Vehicle state bus" as Veh #E8F0FE
participant "Digital-key /\nimmobilizer buses" as Access #FCE8FF
participant "DOOR_FR\nfront-right door owner" as DoorFR #E8F7E8
participant "Door FR state bus" as DoorBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\nbody readers" as Obs #FFF4CC

== Door FR Inputs ==

DoorCtl -> DoorFR : frmDoorControlMsg\nDoorControlCmd
Veh -> DoorFR : frmVehicleStateCanMsg\ngDriveState
Access -> DoorFR : frmDigitalKeyStateMsg\nVehicleAccessState / KeyPresence
Access -> DoorFR : frmImmobilizerStateMsg\nImmobilizerState / KeyAuthState
activate DoorFR
DoorFR -> DoorFR : freshness checks for\ndoor control, vehicle, dkey, immo
DoorFR -> DoorFR : manualMode may read\nChassis::driveState directly
DoorFR -> DoorFR : accessAuthorized =\nparked vehicle and dkey/immo auth valid
DoorFR -> DoorFR : unlockRequest =\nDoorControlCmd > 0
DoorFR -> DoorFR : unlock only when\nauthorized and requested
note right of DoorFR
Representative gating inputs
- DoorControlCmd
- gDriveState
- VehicleAccessState / KeyPresence
- ImmobilizerState / KeyAuthState
end note

== Door FR Publish ==

DoorFR -> DoorBus : frmDoorFrStateMsg\nDoorFrLockState / DoorFrOpenState / DoorFrWindowPos
note right of DoorFR
Representative outputs
- DoorFrLockState
- DoorFrOpenState
- DoorFrWindowPos
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

DoorBus -> Obs : front-door lock visibility /\nbody observers
deactivate DoorFR

note over DoorCtl, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Front-door control, vehicle, digital-key, and immobilizer context reach DOOR_FR
2. DOOR_FR resolves parked-state access authorization
3. Unlock request is gated by access authorization
4. DOOR_FR publishes final front-right door lock state
end note

@enduml
